query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it1.info in ('birth name','copyright holder','LD length','LD spaciality','LD release date','production dates','LD quality of source','other works') AND it2.info in ('LD picture format','release dates','genres','LD review','LD quality of source','LD video artifacts','LD quality program','LD video noise','LD contrast','trade mark','LD pressing plant','LD catalog number','production dates','LD spaciality','LD sound encoding','budget','LD video standard','quotes','languages','studios','screenplay-teleplay') AND n.gender not in ('m') AND (n.name like '%r%' OR n.name like '%i%' OR n.name like '%Q%' OR n.name like '%b%') AND t.production_year > 1996 AND t.production_year < 2010 AND (t.title like '%secret%') AND mi.info in ('Irish Gaelic','Maori','German','Norwegian','Bosnian','French','Portuguese','Kyrgyz','Albanian','Indonesian','Tagalog') AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','crew') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','complete','complete+verified')
